{"tid":1885123,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Mastercard推Tap on Phone　手機接受信用卡收款","createTime":"2020-02-18T05:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T04:11:16.000Z","uid":134993,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e502397d77ab1a1948ef50e4e8646f77d47009ff","tid":1885123,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:28:02.000Z","msg":"Mastercard今日(4日)宣布，夥拍大新銀行及BBPOS MSL，攜手推出全港首個手機程式收款技術「Tap on Phone」，讓本地中小企能透過手機接受感應式支付卡付款。<br />\n<br />\n「Tap on Phone」是一項簡單、快捷的收款技術，本地中小企可以使用任何具NFC功能的Android手機，透過手機程式接受感應式支付卡付款，只需下載一個手機程式便可收款，無需額外硬件，節省時間之餘更可降低成本。中小企商戶可用感應式信用卡、扣帳卡及預付卡、手機錢包及智能手錶付款，有助他們拓展業務。<br />\n<br />\n同時，Mastercard亦首次將其「品牌聲音識別」（Sonic Branding）引入香港，並應用在此全新的收款技術當中。當持卡人在付款時聽到Mastercard專屬的「品牌聲音識別」，便代表着該項交易成功且安全可靠。"},{"pid":"73d553f36c7140d668c8f5929e3d713ccf9fa4a5","tid":1885123,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"即係乜尻"},{"pid":"2f3568459a39f613fbde62174aa2c8d47923744e","tid":1885123,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"Google Pay???"},{"pid":"23af68198b467cecd68d46519a3058eef90ab9fc","tid":1885123,"uid":334553,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"73d553f36c7140d668c8f5929e3d713ccf9fa4a5","tid":1885123,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"即係乜尻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"唔洗用信用卡機， 有部android 電話就收得credit card<br />\n小商戶唔洗租機"},{"pid":"88e60f158e1423aff65ec03862c8f7107e73e4dd","tid":1885123,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f3568459a39f613fbde62174aa2c8d47923744e","tid":1885123,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"Google Pay???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"即商戶可用手機 收apple pay、google pay 等 信用卡支付"},{"pid":"929c1eb3b1cde48d2b26efc83fb0325fd1dc11d3","tid":1885123,"uid":26553